e^{-\frac{sx}{\lambda_{1}}}e^{-\frac{x}{\lambda_{1}\tau}} & 0\\
-\alpha\frac{\lambda_{1}}{\lambda_{2}}\left(e^{-\frac{sx}{\lambda_{1}}}e^{-\frac{x}{\lambda_{1}\tau}}-e^{-\frac{sx}{\lambda_{2}}}\right)\frac{1}{s+\alpha} & e^{-\frac{sx}{\lambda_{2}}}
